<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA50">
<l>pirintoṉṟu nōkkātu tammuṭaiya piṉṉē</l>
<l>tirintuḻaluñ cintaṉaiyār tammai purintorukā</l>
<l>lāvā veṉaviraṅkā rantō valitēkol</l>
<l>māvai piḷantār maṉam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those with minds that, separating, without looking at anything,</l>
<l>roam about after him, will he not long for them one time</l>
<l>[and], ah, feel pity for them, alas? Is it [that] hard,</l>
<l>the heart of him who split the horse[‘s mouth]?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
